dc_title_s: West Indies, Bahamas, Tongue of the Ocean, northern part (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From U.S. charts to 1995, a British Admiralty chart of 1998, and U.S. Navy surveys to 1964." Shipping list no.: 2003-2006-S. "Copyright 2003 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map No.26308 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
